task.summary: * Added a tab, titled "Results". It has to display the search/browse result data. * Clicking the "Search" button in the "Search" fragment now takes you to "Results" * ResultsFragmentTab currently causes a fatal error, the problematic code is commented out
* An early stub for the background access to online and local services.

* Classes moved to packages. * The Tab fragments now have a single superclass to abstract the common features. * Tab IDs are now stored in Enum. * Search string is now passed to the "Results" fragment successfully.
* A few additions to the background task. Still a long way to go though.
* Early groundwork for the "Sentences" model. * Early groundwork for the DataBase entry point.
* Early groundwork for the "Sentences" model. * Early groundwork for the DataBase entry point.
* CSV parsing experiments continued. * Added a splash screen to be displayed while the DB is being initialized for the first time. * Added a working progressBar to the splash screen.
* Added the essential CSV files to initialize the local demo DB
